  <brief_title>Impact of Physiotherapy Intervention for Children With Ankle Sprains</brief_title>
  <official_title>Exploring the Impact of a Physiotherapy Intervention on the Risk of Re-injury and Recovery in Children and Adolescents With Acute Ankle Sprains: a Randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
